  <brief_title>Use of TpCO2 (Transcutaneous CO2 Measurement) as PaCO2 Predictor During NIV in Case of Acute Hypercapnic Respiratory Failure</brief_title>
  <acronym>TpCO2-NIV</acronym>
  <official_title>Use of TpCO2 (Transcutaneous CO2 Measurement)as PaCO2 Predictor During Non Invasive Ventilation (NIV) in Case of Acute Hypercapnic Respiratory Failure</official_title>
